
                This repository is vim config file
=============================================================

  +---------------------------------------------------------+
  |                                                         |
  | I'm looking for a good configuration that make me feel  |
  | like I can fly over my keyboard with vim, whereas I     |
  | save the history of all the changes.                    |
  |                                                         |
  +---------------------------------------------------------+

                          architecture
=============================================================

  +-----------[Attempt to keep one reason of change]--------+
  |                                                         |
  | + plugin: in here I put the plugins configurations.     |
  |                                                         |
  | + plugin/own: in here I put all of my own 'plugins',    |
  |   e.g., my own statusline or my own keybinds.           |
  |                                                         |
  +------------------[see commit 5564a18]-------------------+

  .
  ├── init.vim
  │
  ├── plugin
  │   │
  │   ├── fzf.vim
  │   ├── vim-go.vim
  │   │
  │   └── own
  │       │
  │       ├── keybinds.vim
  │       ├── statusline.vim
  │       .
  │
  ├── README
  │
 
